---
title: Double-Stacked Caramelized Onion Burgers with Garlic Aioli and Baked Cauliflower 'Frites'
description: One of our favourites: the Caramelized Onion Burger – caramelized onions, spinach, soft brioche buns and perfectly packed patties. Roasted cauliflower 'frites' and garlic aioli make the perfect sides.
